{"id": 2120, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都厌倦了哪些工作上的繁文缛节？", "description": "本职工作都不够时间做的，为什么还总要在这些低效又无意义的事上浪费时间。（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 4458, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180115160033ZiEsHJadMPKguOLB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-16T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 259584, "content": "单位里职务稍高的同事在单位以外，比如非正式聚餐，依然自带领导光环试图主导一切。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239449}, {"id": 259585, "content": "明明是因为工作做不好，内部好不好确不知道更换。还在以为的坚守。最终是幻想。新兴时代的八串，希望你能逆流而上，乘风破浪。", "image": "img/option/option/20180116213343UrbISOAdpDlYGV15", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239451}, {"id": 259589, "content": "一个月梳理三次岗位职责，每次都有新发现，优秀???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213027}, {"id": 259592, "content": "认真的吗？！发布消息让回复一下就繁文缛节了？就是领导找存在感了？真的只是想确认一下大家都有收到而已啊！不然强调的事情，你犯错了，一句“我不知道啊。发群里了？我没看见啊”你让领导怎么回你？", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239487}, {"id": 260872, "content": "统计这个统计那个", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212130}, {"id": 259594, "content": "周报月报各种总结报告，复制粘贴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236713}, {"id": 261130, "content": "开各种没效率的会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244984}, {"id": 259595, "content": "明明可以扁平化非要走流程，需要走流程的偏偏不走", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239497}, {"id": 259596, "content": "领导总要把其它汇报过的内容，再重新自己来讲一遍。感觉一场会议没有听到一句是重点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239498}, {"id": 259597, "content": "接电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230985}, {"id": 259599, "content": "垃圾认为自己是金子，非要装出那个逼样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1228271}, {"id": 259600, "content": "做政绩不要业绩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239503}, {"id": 259601, "content": "花很多时间坐ppt表格给领导看", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039130}, {"id": 259602, "content": "1、应酬\n2、总结\n3、制度考试", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234937}, {"id": 259603, "content": "填个表格，15个工作日后再来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814778}, {"id": 259604, "content": "领导不同意，你就不敢再多动作", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174568}, {"id": 259605, "content": "因为领导很啰嗦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239533}, {"id": 259607, "content": "明明只需要发短信通知，非要花一个小时一个个打电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208684}, {"id": 259608, "content": "打卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918502}, {"id": 259609, "content": "请个假，明明人就在眼前，还要走形式", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1214537}, {"id": 259611, "content": "动不动开个会捋流程!", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954783}, {"id": 259612, "content": "讨论半天的结果：改日再议。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216308}, {"id": 259615, "content": "这是个伪命题，80%的工作都是低效率无意义的。哪有那么多创造性的工作等着你。能让繁冗细节变得有趣也是你的本事", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239581}, {"id": 259616, "content": "有建议和意见也不想说。只做份内的事，其他的都只看不说不做不参与", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239590}, {"id": 274209, "content": "请走OAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOAOA", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303540}, {"id": 259617, "content": "报销单，一贴一整天", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 505814}, {"id": 259873, "content": "少谈些主义", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239772}, {"id": 259618, "content": "每天都重复的回答同样的问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239596}, {"id": 260387, "content": "每天都要挑战一个新的工种！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152136}, {"id": 259622, "content": "什么事情都是沟通沟通，最后还是照旧，忙的忙死，闲的闲死。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190212}, {"id": 259623, "content": "同业对标，班组对标，工作评价指标，各种指标。。。嫩是不是闲得蛋疼？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239683}, {"id": 259629, "content": "做毫无意义与价值的图文资料，只是为了应付检查。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948110}, {"id": 260653, "content": "最搞笑以前单位的女领导。喜欢天天打鸡血的培训 目标不要收入也要努力干活", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097424}, {"id": 259630, "content": "明明只是契约关系，却搞得像奴主关系。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239703}, {"id": 259633, "content": "日报，周报，月报，季度报，日报要精确到分钟，喵喵喵。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115782}, {"id": 259635, "content": "开不完的会  说来说去都是同一句废话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013508}, {"id": 259636, "content": "宁可每周多加班20小时也不愿意优化工作流程提高一下正常工作时间内的工作效率", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234320}, {"id": 259637, "content": "成本和效率之间要做个权衡，领导和服从之间也有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141976}, {"id": 259638, "content": "中午吃饭的时候，老板总是喜欢聊自己，需要我们迎合…尬聊真的很影响食欲…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013404}, {"id": 259894, "content": "明明电脑可以搞定的事非要手写，还不许涂改不许写错不许设备名称错", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240521}, {"id": 259639, "content": "无意义的加班?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234449}, {"id": 259640, "content": "每年一次的总结，必须上台读！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670012}, {"id": 259641, "content": "已经写了周志，开会的时候还要汇报这周都干了啥。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222582}, {"id": 259642, "content": "小公司没活干，天天当空气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1073444}, {"id": 259898, "content": "在吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240568}, {"id": 259644, "content": "公司不论什么层级的人都用“您”称呼对方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238977}, {"id": 259645, "content": "什么东西讨论完了都要邮件确认 邮件要永远存档留证保护自己拿去扯皮 老板会说重要的东西要贴在正文不够只是附件 邮件要前后贯通", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059247}, {"id": 259901, "content": "开会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1237615}, {"id": 259646, "content": "策划和执行注定相爱相杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1232434}, {"id": 259649, "content": "写市场部方案，大伙讨论开口闭口都是x总在什么会上说过要这么做，x总不喜欢怎么做，今年流行xxx销售理念，完全无视市场分析和客户需求", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198563}]}